Alternate Repeat Pattern

#The program must accept a positive even integer N as the input.
#The program must print the desired pattern as shown in the Example Input/Output section.

#Example:
Input:
6
Output:
1666666
2255555
3334444

#code
n=int(input())
for i in range(1,(n//2)+1):
    for j in range(i):
        print(i,end="")
    for k in range(n):
        print(n,end="")
    n=n-1
    print()
